<lb ed="I" n="0244b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0244b0101">夫理<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">貫</unclear>沖寂。非聾俗<note n="0244001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30479"/>＝所【史】</note><note n="0244001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30479"/>【佛拓】，所【史】</note><app n="0244001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>聞。真<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">假</unclear>□資。詎是六識□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辯</unclear>。莫不□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b02" type="honorific"/>火輪騖。風爓<note n="0244002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">飃＝飄【史】</note><note n="0244002" resp="ihp" type="mod">飃【佛拓】，飄【史】</note><app n="0244002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">飄</lem><rdg wit="【原】">飃</rdg></app>遷。娑婆寸陰之晷。徘徊永劫之路。自神光□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b03" type="honorific"/>夢。化洽群生。經教遺象。咸歸讚誦。聞片義而涉道場。受五□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b04" type="honorific"/>而昇彼岸。清信士女楊暎香。任買女等。邑義八十人。雖容□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b05" type="honorific"/>未改。而戒德□<note n="0244003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB10485"/>＝弘【史】</note><note n="0244003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB10485"/>【佛拓】，弘【史】</note><app n="0244003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">弘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB10485"/></rdg></app>。既悟形非定質。且覺眾緣□聚。□火不□。
<lb ed="I" n="0244b06" type="honorific"/>四微乃異。燕肝越膽。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">未</unclear>足為喻。想毗耶而<note n="0244004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31101"/>＝聳【史】</note><note n="0244004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31101"/>【佛拓】，聳【史】</note><app n="0244004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聳</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31101"/></rdg></app><note n="0244005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31102"/>＝轡【史】</note><note n="0244005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31102"/>【佛拓】，轡【史】</note><app n="0244005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">轡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31102"/></rdg></app>。望<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">波</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">斯</unclear>而□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b07" type="honorific"/><note n="0244006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨋎＝軫【史】</note><note n="0244006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨋎【佛拓】，軫【史】</note><app n="0244006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨋎</rdg></app>。並割捨肌膚之外。敬造涅槃經一部。覆匱之心。起於大□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b08" type="honorific"/>河清之祀。繕寫<note n="0244007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30675"/>＝裝【史】</note><note n="0244007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30675"/>【佛拓】，裝【史】</note><app n="0244007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">裝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30675"/></rdg></app>飾。至天統五年歲在己丑秋八月。剋就□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b09" type="honorific"/><note n="0244008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30779"/>＝願【史】</note><note n="0244008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30779"/>【佛拓】，願【史】</note><app n="0244008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30779"/></rdg></app>。製像四龕。因碑建<note n="0244009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">号＝號【史】</note><note n="0244009" resp="ihp" type="mod">号【佛拓】，號【史】</note><app n="0244009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">號</lem><rdg wit="【原】">号</rdg></app>。採石求匠。事未有成。遇縣令楊君。□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b10" type="honorific"/>悟獨曉。善於開導。君字景信。<app type="star" corresp="#0244003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">弘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB10485"/></rdg></app>農人也。爰自<note n="0244010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">莅＝蒞【史】</note><note n="0244010" resp="ihp" type="mod">莅【佛拓】，蒞【史】</note><app n="0244010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蒞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">莅</rdg></app>止。流惠為□。
<lb ed="I" n="0244b11" type="honorific"/>下被民和。上宣聖澤。挹貪水而逾清。處脂膏而轉潔。既泯□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b12" type="honorific"/>晝擾。大息夜<note n="0244011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">嚻＝囂【史】</note><note n="0244011" resp="ihp" type="mod">嚻【佛拓】，囂【史】</note><app n="0244011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">囂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">嚻</rdg></app>。來晚之詠。事不容口。又復納□之餘。垂心□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b13" type="honorific"/>法。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">遂</unclear>擇一顯敞之地。擬類祇園之<app type="star" corresp="#0244001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>。卻背獸嶺。前帶黃津。□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b14" type="honorific"/>據鳳臺。西居<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">永</unclear>禁。今經始畢功。實蒙勸獎。尊麗自天。形非□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b15" type="honorific"/>造。刊勒徽<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">音</unclear>。載傳不朽。其詞曰
<lb ed="I" n="0244b16" type="honorific"/>法炬開朗。惠照閻浮。淨持三昧。競捨<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">簞</unclear>□。皮紙應化。骨筆□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b17" type="honorific"/>流。劫云將盡。天衣未伓。<note place="inline">其一</note>
<lb ed="I" n="0244b18" type="honorific"/>四<note n="0244012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虵＝蛇【史】</note><note n="0244012" resp="ihp" type="mod">虵【佛拓】，蛇【史】</note><app n="0244012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虵</rdg></app>吐毒。二<note n="0244013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣆨＝鼠【史】</note><note n="0244013" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣆨【佛拓】，鼠【史】</note><app n="0244013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣆨</rdg></app>侵株。眷言苦海。沈溺須<note n="0244014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB17688"/>＝臾【史】</note><note n="0244014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB17688"/>【佛拓】，臾【史】</note><app n="0244014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">臾</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB17688"/></rdg></app>。敬<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">憑</unclear>介福。<note n="0244015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31103"/>＝撤【史】</note><note n="0244015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31103"/>【佛拓】，撤【史】</note><app n="0244015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">撤</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31103"/></rdg></app>施□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b19" type="honorific"/>廬。邑同<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">詰</unclear>士。義等文殊。<note place="inline">其二</note>
<lb ed="I" n="0244b20" type="honorific"/>雕碑刊聖。刻妙真容。當來即是。過去成□。楊□宰邑。道<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">俗</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0244b21" type="honorific"/>恭。恩超春日。德茂寒松。<note place="inline">其三</note>
<lb ed="I" n="0244b22" type="honorific"/>　大齊武平元年歲在庚寅十一月庚戌朔十四日癸亥</p>
